      bsp-remove-layout; bsp-cache-layout; bsp-layout once tall; polybar-msg action "#bspwm.hook.1"; notify-send -e -u low -t 2000 "Master Layout (OneShot)"

# Reverse Master Stack Layout (OneShot)
